BUILD FROM SCRATCH INSTRUCTIONS
--------------------------------

create flutter project directory

change directory into project directory

create a folder in the root folder, for vs-code, name ".devcontainer"

    mkdir .devcontainer

change directory into ".devcontainer"

create a file named "devcontainer.json

    touch devcontainer.json

create folder, in the root folder, for vs-code, named "workspace".

    mkdir workspace

create a "Dockerfile" in the root folder.

    touch Dockerfile


VS CONTAINER TERMINAL
----------------------

run 'flutter doctor'

	flutter doctor



